description.excerpt:
R<sup>3</sup>Det is based on Focal Loss for Dense Object Detection, and it is completed by YangXue. 
More results and trained models are available in the MODEL_ZOO.md.
The performance of all models comes from the source paper.

installation.excerpt: 2、(Recommend in this repo) Or you can choose to use a better backbone, refer to gluon2TF.
